      <br>
        <div id="panel">
        <h2 class="display-8">Intern in Investment Banking</h2>
        <p class="lead text-justify">
          The Investment Banking division of Danareksa helps companies and governments by raising funds through issuing
          and selling securities in the capital markets (both equity and bond),
          as well as providing advice on transactions such as mergers and acquisitions.
          In funds raising business, clients can derive value from our recognized strength in capital resources as well as extensive network among domestic and global financial institutions,
           which make for a successful underwriting exercise, from book building process up to the sale of securities.
     <br>
     <br>
             In 2015, I was interning at <i>Investment Banking Danareksa Securities</i> in which I
          learned on the technique of updating business research every morning from newspapers and
          summarize information that related to corporate clients. Other than that, this internship also
          thought me how to analyze the mining industry (such as understanding the pricing condition and
          how to estimate the price of goods in the mining industry), perform <i>DuPont analysis calculation</i>
          task for client investment prospects (such as understanding how to calculate with <i>DuPont
          analysis</i>), and doing the task of inputting client company financial report data for the past 5
          years (understanding how to compile financial statement). Beyond the tasks that I was given, I
          have also received training in <i>financial modeling</i> in which it thought me how to input data to
          excel, <i>Bloomberg application</i> to understand how to use the application properly for early user,
          and received lecture regarding the introduction of capital market presented by Mr. Jenpino, the
          President Director of <i>Danareksa Securities</i>. From this experience, I also gained knowledge on
          how to prepare documents before an important meeting with clients. From this intern
          program, I gained plenty of new financial skill that has never been thought in school, as well as
          understanding the office environment. I’m glad I could be a part of <i>Investment Banking
          Danareksa Securities</i>, which provided me knowledge and experience that I’ve never had before.
        </p>
