        <p class="lead text-justify">
         In 2014, <a href="https://id.linkedin.com/in/gamaldhana" target="_blank">Gamal Ramadhana</a>, <i>Founder of Galeri Tie Dye</i> and one of my college friends asked me to help him run his business.
        I was very excited when he explained <i>Galeri Tie Dye's</i> Segmentation, Targeting, and Positioning <i>(STP)</i> and it made me want to be a part of it, along with his unique and brilliant idea. With that offer, <i>Galeri Tie Dye</i> has become one of the first businesses that I had experience in taking care of.
        We were not the only ones who ran Galeri Tie Dye, there also <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alriosuyoso/?originalSubdomain=id" target="_blank">Alrio Gaputra Suyoso</a> as<i> Founder of Galeri Tie Dye and Director of Marketing</i>,
